OL,4,Cnow 'growing stronger every day'
OL,6,F"But then I saw her stomach move and
OL,7,Fknew instantly she was pregnant, and I
OL,8,Fhad to act quickly to give the babies
OL,9,Fa chance at life."
OL,11,FThe farmer delivered two tiny leverets
OL,12,Fby the side of the road after using a
OL,13,Fpen knife to perform an emergency
OL,14,Fcaesarean section procedure. The
OL,15,Fsecond baby hare did not survive its
OL,16,Fbirth.
OL,18,FHe added: "I carefully cut them open
OL,19,Fand saw the babies. I gave them a
OL,20,Fgentle swing to clear out any mucus,
OL,21,Fjust like you would with newborn lambs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]
