OL,3,CHare who survived caesarean birth is
OL,4,Cnow 'growing stronger every day'
OL,6,F"Then I started rubbing their bodies
OL,7,Fto try and get them breathing, and
OL,8,Fsure enough, they gasped and came
OL,9,Faround. So, I stopped working, got
OL,10,Fthem warmed up and called the Scottish
OL,11,FSPCA."
OL,13,FBruno has been on the road to recovery
OL,14,Fwith help from Scottish SPCA staff at
OL,15,Fthe National Wildlife Rescue Centre.
OL,16,FHe was admitted underweight at just
OL,17,F80g, below the typical 100-130g birth
OL,18,Fweight for a newborn hare.
