OL,3,CHare who survived caesarean birth is
OL,4,Cnow 'growing stronger every day'
OL,6,F"He was feeding well and showed great
OL,7,Fenergy, so I knew I needed to get him
OL,8,Fto our team at Fishcross as quickly as
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,F"We stopped a couple of times on the
OL,12,Fjourney for feeds, and each time he
OL,13,Fdid brilliantly.
OL,15,FWe were all amazed he had survived
OL,16,Fsuch a dramatic start to life.
