OL,3,CHare who survived caesarean birth is
OL,4,Cnow 'growing stronger every day'
OL,6,F"It's heartwarming to know that thanks
OL,7,Fto a kind-hearted farmer, the wildlife
OL,8,Fcentre team, and myself, this little
OL,9,Fmiracle will get the chance to return
OL,10,Fto the wild and live a full life."
OL,12,FBruno's carer, Shauni Stoddart says he
OL,13,Fwas in a "very fragile condition" at
OL,14,Ffirst. The Wildlife Assistant said:
OL,15,F"Due to his unique circumstances, he
OL,16,Fwas hand-reared at home for the first
OL,17,Ffive days to minimise stress. He
OL,18,Fresponded incredibly well, quickly
OL,19,Fgaining strength.
