OL,3,CHare who survived caesarean birth is
OL,4,Cnow 'growing stronger every day'
OL,6,F"It's been an emotional journey for
OL,7,Feveryone involved but seeing him grow
OL,8,Fstronger every day is so rewarding."
OL,10,FNow nine times his original weight,
OL,11,Fthe team is optimistic that Bruno will
OL,12,Fbe ready for release in the coming
OL,13,Fweeks, provided his progress continues.
OL,15,FThe Scottish SPCA does not encourage
OL,16,Fanyone to perform this type of surgery
OL,17,Fon any animal.
